column5: My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers. Beautiful ranch with gorgeous views. Sit quiet enough and see different wild animals roaming the property. I have 4 bedrooms upstairs that are available. This room is a private room with a Jack-n-Jill bathroom connecting to Room 2 This is a Nikken Wellness home. A Nikken Wellness Home offers comfortable, quality rest and relaxation along with cleaner, more healthy air and water.
